        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves </strong>from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop your <strong>dates</strong> roughly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1637144304066-x200.jpg",
