    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>giant couscous </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>giant couscous</strong> for 8 min or until tender with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot</p><p>Fluff with a fork before serving</p>",
