    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is nearly ready, add your <strong>pumpkin seeds </strong>to the baking tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 3 min or until the pumpkin seeds are toasted and the aubergine is golden and slightly charred</p><p>Tip: Watch the seeds like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p>",
