    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>sliced cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped dates</strong>,<strong> mint</strong> and <strong>coriander </strong>to the bowl with the softened giant couscous</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and season very generously with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>herby giant couscous salad</strong></p>",
