      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>herby</strong> <strong>giant couscous salad </strong>with a dollop of <strong>butter bean hummus </strong>to the side</p><p>Top with the<strong> pomegranate-glazed aubergine </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>toasted pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
